Background

		Mr. Jon M. Plexico is the Founder, General Partner and Managing Member at Stonepine Capital Management LLC. Mr. Plexico served as Managing Director and Vice President of Merriman Capital, Inc. (alternate name Merriman Curhan Ford & Co.), where he ran the healthcare corporate finance division and focused on private investments in public equity (PIPEs), secondary offerings and mergers and acquisitions. Mr. Plexico was a Co-Founding Partner at Venture Ready Partners. Mr. ... Plexico served as Director of Business Development at NexPrise, Inc. (alternate name Chemdex Corporation). He began his career at Quidel Corporation and served as its National Sales Manager of autoimmune & complement division. He has been a Director of Viveve Medical, Inc. since March 14, 2016 and Zila, Inc. since April 2009. Mr. Plexico has a Bachelor of Arts Degree in Political Science from Colgate University.Read Full Background




